snippet.title: Batyr: The Tale of the Brave - teaser trailer
snippet.description:
Hi everyone! The first teaser trailer of our project - Batyr: Tale of the Brave. 

The plot will touch on Turkic mythology and culture. The player will be able to visit the open world, explore a variety of biomes and experience a unique combat system.
